account.descriptionLink:
Since the protocol can now handle pegged $USDC domain name registration prices, we should revisit all the Pricing Plans for all the Pools.

In the interest of a faster and more seamless process, this proposal states:

FOR THIS ONCE, and for a limited time, the Pool Initiator can decide on the new $USDC Pricing Structure

Any subsequent Repricing Requests will need to pass a >51% Pooled $ALL contribution check to be validated
